{"tid":1658633,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"岑子杰事件的另外睇法","createTime":"2019-10-16T14:22:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-17T05:33:29.000Z","uid":260371,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"71ec13e150122df6933d06a92a97d40e9ec3424f","tid":1658633,"uid":260371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T14:22:14.000Z","msg":"手動轉<br />\n<br />\n岑子杰遇襲，雖然表面同民陣申請遊行有關，但係岑子杰同時係瀝源選區區議會候選人，而最近區議會候選人多宗受襲事件：<br />\n<br />\n10月8日：梁凱晴觀塘遇襲；<br />\n10月12日：仇栩欣炮台山遇襲；<br />\n10月16日：岑子杰旺角遇襲。<br />\n<br />\n「平均4日1單！」<br />\n<br />\n而岑子杰選區有一棟相當特別嘅建築物，多年來屹立不倒，內裡娛樂場所林立，而當中有一個熟悉嘅品牌名字。。。<br />\n<br />\n而呢個品牌同咩省份組織有聯繫相信大家都記憶猶新。<br />\n<br />\n而如果岑子杰當選，會對呢棟建築帶來咩影響呢？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eQBhKoy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeQBhKoy.jpg&h=e90cdde3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4f14f9f071561ba2b920659725c5426f96c4568d","tid":1658633,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T14:23:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你幾時裝修我多數都支持你地！<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">1017支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1018支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1019支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1020我屌你老母, 難得食個勢搞百萬行, 見返818個感覺返曬嚟, 一大班5毛就出嚟帶風向<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">1021支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n..............</blockquote><br />\n星期日大遊行改做裝修？不了！我話你聽點解。<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1658541\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1658541</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">好嬲？聽日要見到文宣砌成o既10.20, 你先對得住岑子杰<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">同埋保持憤怒, 今個星期是文宣週 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">星期日是和理非主場, 過埋星期日反佢枱</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d7oHaWT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd7oHaWT.jpg&h=75f2ea83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【再次有圖有真相】令街坊知道1020遊行嘅最佳方法<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1657842\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1657842</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"454737c883e69f187883cfb1b3f106341c00504e","tid":1658633,"uid":288154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T05:33:29.000Z","msg":"終於明白 襲擊子杰【真正目的】<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1659465\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1659465</a>"}]}